<HL>
   Who's News:
   USG Names Connolly
   To Posts of Chairman
   And Chief Executive
</HL>
<DATE>
05/10/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B7
</SO>
<CO>
   USG WNEWS
</CO>
<IN>
BUILDING MATERIALS (BLD)
</IN>
<LP>
   CHICAGO -- The board of USG Corp. elected Eugene B.
Connolly, who has been president and chief executive officer,
to the posts of chairman and chief executive officer.
   Anthony J. Falvo Jr., currently executive vice president
and chief operating officer, was elected president and chief
operating officer. Both changes take effect June 1.
</LP>
<TEXT>
   Robert J. Day, currently chairman of the board, will
continue in that post until his retirement May 31.
   USG manufactures and distributes building materials.
</TEXT>
